						<summary>

						<p>Last portion is badly damaged. Records the gift of land at Śiṟṟaḷundūr in Tirumalai Kāṅgēyaṉ sīrmai <hi rend="italic">alias</hi> Śiṟṟaḷundūr of Mōrūr, situated in Ēḻugarai Pūnduṟai nāḍu by one Sāma Nāyaṉār, an agent of Triyambaka uḍaiyār who was ruling over Muḷvāy Eyinūrchchāvaḍi.</p>						

						</summary>
